[gd_scene load_steps=12 format=3]

; Miami / Vice City — THE game map. The streamer pages real Miami districts
; (downtown, Brickell, South Beach, Mid-Beach, Wynwood) from the manifest at
; their true offsets. Warm late-afternoon Vice City grade. No SDFGI (it flickers
; as districts page in); sky-sourced ambient + SSR/SSIL carry the bounce.

